!! !!Consonant gradation rules

"Consonant Gradation for htt(j|s):ht(j|s)"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
t:0 <=> Vow: h t _ ( j | s ) (Vow:+) (Cns:+) ( Dummy: ) WeG: ;

! !!€ áhttje^WG
! !!€ áht0je0

"Consonant Gradation for hxx:hx"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Cx:0 <=> Vow: h Cx _ (Vow:+) (Cns:+) ( Dummy: ) WeG: ;
     where Cx in (p k) ; ! 't' covered by "Consonant Gradation for htt(j|s):ht(j|s)"

! !!€ náhppe^WG
! !!€ náhp0e0

"Consonant Gradation for xdn(j):xn(j)"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
d:0 <=> Vow: Cx _ n (j) Vow: Cns:* ( Dummy: ) WeG: ;
     where Cx in ( j v l ) ;

