"Final Consonant Deletion"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Cx:0 <=> _ (Dummy:) %^CDEL: ;
	where Cx in ( b d g s h ) ; ! JW: added h (riebe/riehpeha); what about j (båtsoj/buhtsu)??

! !!€ riehpeh^WG^CDEL
! !!€ rie0be000
! 
! !!€ biednag^WG^CDEL
