"Final devoicing"
!! __@RULENAME@__  
Cx:Cy <=> _ .#. ;
    where Cx in ( b2 d2 g2 )
          Cy in ( p  t  k  )
          matched ; ! JW: removed pair h2:j (not sure what it refers to)

