!! ! Monophthong rules 

"á to ä and å to u and a to i in front u and i"
Vx:Vy <=> [Cns|#:] _ Cns:*  [:u|:i] (%^WG:0) %>: j %^MONB4J:0 ;
          [Cns|#:] _ Cns:*  i %^IUML:0   ;
	where Vx in (a á å)
	      Vy in (i ä u)
	      matched ;
	      ! båtsoj>buhttsu, rássjo>rässjuj,árrbe>ärbujn, gallgat>gilgiv, åbba>ubbijda 	      

!Vx:Vy <=> [Cns|#:] _ Cns:*  [a:|e:|o:] (%^WG:0) %>: %^MONB4J:0 j ;


"á to ä in ij forms"
 á:ä <=> _ Cns:+ Vow: %^WG:0 %^IJ:0 %>:0 j ;

